| Column          | Type     | Description                                         |
| --------------- | -------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| Unnamed: 0      | integer  | Index column created during preprocessing.          |
| SEGMENT_ID      | integer  | Unique identifier for each roadway traffic segment. |
| SPEED           | float    | Observed average vehicle speed in miles per hour.   |
| TRAVEL_TIME     | float    | Estimated time required to traverse the segment.    |
| LENGTH          | float    | Length of the roadway segment in meters.            |
| STREET          | string   | Name of the street where the segment is located.    |
| DIRECTION       | string   | Cardinal travel direction (N, S, E, W).             |
| FROM_STREET     | string   | Starting cross street of the segment.               |
| TO_STREET       | string   | Ending cross street of the segment.                 |
| STREET_HEADING  | string   | Textual orientation of the segment.                 |
| BUS_COUNT       | float    | Number of buses detected in that interval.          |
| MESSAGE_COUNT   | float    | Number of sensor or probe messages sent.            |
| RECORD_ID       | float    | Identifier for the traffic measurement record.      |
| START_LATITUDE  | float    | Latitude coordinate at the start of the segment.    |
| START_LONGITUDE | float    | Longitude coordinate at the start of the segment.   |
| END_LATITUDE    | float    | Latitude coordinate at the end of the segment.      |
| END_LONGITUDE   | float    | Longitude coordinate at the end of the segment.     |
| COMMENTS        | string   | Additional notes from the source dataset.           |
| START_LOCATION  | string   | Human readable start location.                      |
| END_LOCATION    | string   | Human readable end location.                        |
| TEMP            | float    | Temperature in degrees Celsius.                     |
| PRCP            | float    | Precipitation in millimeters.                       |
| HMDT            | float    | Relative humidity percentage.                       |
| WND_DIR         | float    | Wind direction in degrees.                          |
| WND_SPD         | float    | Wind speed in meters per second.                    |
| ATM_PRESS       | float    | Atmospheric pressure in hPa.                        |
| Pm2.5           | float    | Fine particulate matter (microns < 2.5).            |
| Pm10            | float    | Coarse particulate matter (microns < 10).           |
| No2             | float    | Nitrogen dioxide concentration.                     |
| So2             | float    | Sulfur dioxide concentration.                       |
| Co              | float    | Carbon monoxide concentration.                      |
| O3              | float    | Ozone concentration.                                |
| Aqi             | float    | Air Quality Index value.                            |
| TIME            | datetime | Timestamp of observation.                           |
| DATE            | date     | Date extracted from TIME.                           |
| YEAR            | integer  | Year extracted from TIME.                           |
| MONTH           | integer  | Month extracted from TIME.                          |
| DAY_OF_WEEK     | string   | Day name extracted from TIME.                       |
| HOUR            | integer  | Hour of day extracted from TIME.                    |
